descriptionHtml:
[size=3][font=Comic Sans MS]This mod is meant to be played with following mods,becaouse they are together compatible
and expand Whiterun significantly.The following mods :[/font]
 - [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89523]Chapels Of Skyrim[/url] [font=Comic Sans MS][i](Chapel of Kynareth is in Whiterun)[/i][/font]
 - [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89636]Tailors Of Skyrim[/url] [font=Comic Sans MS][i](Tailor Shop in Whiterun)[/i][/font]
 - [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89795]College Of W.,Whiterun Subsidary[/url] [font=Comic Sans MS][i](Which is located in Whiterun)
[/i][/font]
[font=Comic Sans MS]The Different Whiterun itself,adds an Outskirts kind of Suburbs which consists of five houses
and also Great Bazaar And Motel at the outskirts of Whiterun.
There are also Bee Hives at Battle-Born Farm and Nazeem has home just behing A.Cauldron.[/font]

[font=Comic Sans MS]The following mods are also addapted and their Compatible Version are in download section.[/font]
 1. [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56319/]Bordeciel Bank[/url]
 2. [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10509]School Of Knowledge And Youth[/url]
[font=Comic Sans MS]It is also recommended that you download them with those mentioned above.[/font][/size]


[font=Comic Sans MS][size=3][u][b][color=#000000]Version 2.0 -[/color][/b][/u] I fixed many bugs that you guys have been reporting.Also bazaar has better look,and I
added the slums disctrict,which is north up hill from  the entrance zone.The slums consists of following objects :
 - Fortune Teller Shack
 - Skooma Lab
 - Thieves Guild Den
 - Appartment Building which is thou unfinished,thus by locked
 - Two Shacks for One Night Rent

[/size][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=3][i][b][u]Fiule Immersive Whiterun COMP. -[/u][/b][/i] is an patched version of E.T.A.C Immersive Whiterun.It is compatible with Different Whiterun itself,but not with other mods named above.
[/size][/font]
